Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.34,0:01:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still going to pilot it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.54,0:01:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.60,0:01:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People will just hate me even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.21,0:01:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never done anything wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but people have always treated me like a foreigner and hated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I accepted it and thought it made sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:01:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.90,0:01:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.53,0:02:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already in junior high, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.12,0:02:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Rotten Tuna uploaded a new song!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.75,0:02:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold your horses! I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.57,0:02:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fleur, don't just sit there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.88,0:02:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I update my blog where I please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.45,0:02:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, please answer if it's ringing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I poured too much coffee, so I don't have a free hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:02:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Triton. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I got myself into some trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.51,0:03:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad hates Noah, so I hid him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Noah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do now, Ao?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where I go, I'll stand out because of my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to stay away from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:52.66,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,{ao}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Make them stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru! You need to go back to the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's his fault that our island ended up like this—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitoga, take him to my training room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's pretty smart to think of this place. No outsiders will be able to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the islanders all know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all played here when we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No luck. It won't budge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it have some special Japanese military lock?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Japs didn't engineer it by themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They bought the other parts from the Americans and the French.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means this thing is fat, surrenders when possible, and has terrible teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out, Pippo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:04:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to magically make it work—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell did that foreigner kid pilot it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.77,0:05:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that kid could fly an FP before elementary school. He learned all by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To get the person who can pilot this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he said he's not going to pilot it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He will. Oh yes, he will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We see you often in the news, but now we've got the real thing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genere... Generan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Generation Bleu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.49,0:05:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the blue generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that! You're like the Ghostbusters for G-Monsters, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you've even got a cartoon about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Pied Piper, right? You help people in trouble, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young lady, these people have already done their parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be fine with negotiations without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, I'm bringing Allelujah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.33,0:06:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allelujah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.49,0:06:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My IFO!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.31,0:06:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's true that only children can pilot IFOs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,0:06:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Ao yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ao?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the pilot of the IFO yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a rumor...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's so fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! What about the meeting with the SDF?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be more drinking than talking anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the decision making to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:07:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the second Scub Coral that the Okinawa and Ryukyu Alliance have acquired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot allow research to be conducted on something so precious by outsiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Scub Coral hasn't been completely destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's not dealt with, another Secret will emerge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's what you scientists call G-Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.14,0:07:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Secret, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never in my life heard of Secrets showing up at the same place twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We wish you a safe trip home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you finished negotiating with the SDF?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here for our team's Elena Peoples.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Join Fleur. Keep an eye on Scub Coral from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, Miss Rebecca?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.46,0:07:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.94,0:07:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sing a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as the Quartz is still intact, Secrets will show up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You alien kid! Are you a spy for the Japs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My giant?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only know about the sea giant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a big rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not asking you about a rock! We're talking about the giant you pilo—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, Ao.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have we met before?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.75,0:09:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I frequented old Fukai's place ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother was still around at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told them many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get involved with a woman from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... It was thirteen years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then... Mitsuo saw it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.90,0:10:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao's mother fell out of the empty sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was before our Independence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Americans came looking for her, but Fukai Toshio hid her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Ao was born, everyone thought he was an alien...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.90,0:10:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's hated because of that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman and his son brought disaster upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They angered the sea giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea giant?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you were around three, a Scub Burst happened nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, at that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's also when the Americans found your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.14,0:11:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was taken away and the Burst left with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gossiped about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It all happened because she angered the sea giant."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"She summoned the Scub Coral."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could that be my... or my mother's fault?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, a few families who were on an excursion got caught up in the burst,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:12:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the only one who survived was Arata's child, Naru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why I'm hated?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then tell me, what should I have done instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.21,0:12:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could I have done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.98,0:12:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.43,0:12:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't forgive you or your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,So a trapar bubble emerged with the Scub Coral?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,Isn't that good a good thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,That whole profiteering was crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We even lost fishing rights to China during the negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The island was a total mess back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.98,0:12:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The island has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The previous generation wanted to find someone to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do some fucking justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:13:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does Generation Bleu want from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I once knew a girl with turquoise hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know what color the boy's mother's hair was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.97,0:13:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you start that IFO? The Nirvash.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvash?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a girl who called it that. Nirvash.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in! Don't just stand there! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jiro! What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.52,0:13:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Gazelle's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Gazelle's dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know nothing about Jiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:13:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Gazelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.93,0:14:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my real name!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Real my ass, stupid son!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.34,0:14:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use him to negotiate with the Japs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for the sake of Okinawa's true independence!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you out of your mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We bullied him for being a foreigner when we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because our parents... the adults said so!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"He's a foreigner!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"He's an alien!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It's all his and his mother's fault!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't fish? Our independence is half-assed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We blamed it all on Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.14,0:14:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But did you refuse the security money for the Scub?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You children don't understand! Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want independence?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From Japan? From America? From China?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just talk about it! Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch. We'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what the heck is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a G-Monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy shit, it's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Dad and the others be able to get away in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.53,0:15:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can all burn in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me to protect the island yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Aren't you on our side?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, keep your mouth shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pilot that IFO again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.09,0:16:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go to war with the Japs and the Yankees!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.34,0:16:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.47,0:16:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna pilot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up like this because I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put me down at my grandpa's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.11,0:16:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're... Ao...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hate them. You mustn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.15,0:16:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they set our house on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.76,0:16:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, you cannot hate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The adults were all born on this island and they will die on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.45,0:16:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have nowhere else to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They love this island. They just want to protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sorry..." So that's why he apologized...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.07,0:17:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.29,0:17:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, run.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the sea, if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I have every right to love this island too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge! Aim wherever you want! Just hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:18:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Generation Bleu. They're offering us some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put them through.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon our earlier actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No worries. We are going to open fire at the G-Monster now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.83,0:18:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Secret will unleash a powerful electromagnetic burst in the area, rendering your electronics useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conventional projectiles will cause it to react and be countered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conventional weaponry is useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.84,0:18:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been telling everyone this for at least a decade, and they don't get it! Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Secrets' reactions are slow compared to FP's and IFO's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only IFOs in the area are the two of ours...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's three.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our headquarters are negotiating a new contract with the Okinawan government.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But our analysis shows that the signals from the Scub Burst earlier are still present.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.24,0:18:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, our team Pied Piper will now engage and annihilate the Secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.73,0:19:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zone mapping complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some parts are always outside of the zones. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrie, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Support cannons: full power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It can't see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at the feet of the Scub, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! You've got two!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:19:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take them out, so watch out for the shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.91,0:20:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's next.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an entire army.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say you're not going to pilot it? What's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.75,0:20:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight the G-Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too big!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.65,0:20:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you consider yesterday's one to be a \Nfighter, then this one's the mothership!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to protect them? The retarded adults who treated you like shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.93,0:20:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to pilot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.23,0:20:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do, I'll be an alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I don't, I'll regret it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like your dad did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.13,0:20:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to apologize to a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.48,0:21:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.93,0:21:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move, Ao.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.52,0:21:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will make Nirvash remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvash?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.72,0:21:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... you remembered me this entire time...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.04,0:22:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be continued!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.66,0:24:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Eureka Seven AO.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.32,0:24:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To protect the island, Ao throws himself in the battle to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.50,0:24:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His determination shakes people one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.55,0:24:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will the boy do as beyond hope and despair, he loses a place to return to?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.90,0:24:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,Eureka Seven AO, episode 4: Walk This Way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.07,0:24:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen the voice of the children of the stars.
